{"tid":358954,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人家長一昧叫子女讀書，只有讀書先叫正經事","createTime":"2017-08-14T05:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T12:37:00.000Z","uid":28614,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4462033cc76c1f5e3804b71d1d2932cae54a221","tid":358954,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:48:08.000Z","msg":"打波又話「無用」，乜群體活動都話掛住玩，唔正經 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n辛苦讀完六年中學，到入左大學啦又話人地啲仔女自己負責學費生活費，又要你去做 pt 搵錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似完全唔記得左你個學生身分"},{"pid":"0fdf6e323e1789da20409ad4e25972a0ddfbabd0","tid":358954,"uid":28614,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"最後得個垃圾大學學位，書讀唔叻，運動又唔善長，樂器更加無掂過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住 hall 上莊 exchange 出國旅行都未試過，連大學畢業想去台灣 Grad Trip 都被屋企人話「未搵錢先駛錢」"},{"pid":"605a0e1dc0e995ace0b19c7077b536915e18d800","tid":358954,"uid":28614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"即將畢業，聽得最多既說話就係：「第時返工打算比幾多成家用？」"},{"pid":"672a8be5286f91267c99e54292eada2ca2be4e61","tid":358954,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"中學無錢出席交際活動，大學無 hall 住無莊上，識唔到熟既 frd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93073f2664ac92ea2afade5cc5a8a9dad47123f3","tid":358954,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"你唔住hell 上莊姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e46033d8f27b011f0578407adcc75fbabedda9a","tid":358954,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:56:06.000Z","msg":"同你地話輸在起跑線咪同一價值觀，都係金錢同物質最上主義"},{"pid":"f5979ca70105cf963bee76e987cd88a84c789c74","tid":358954,"uid":28614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:57:27.000Z","