},{"pid":"ea4605200d99f1d8ee69db1463d23ad65b50798a","tid":358954,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"當年元首提倡優生學真係無做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">窮人生仔正仆街！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1b902b9e721ce1a885f3fef82e5613d3689c401d","tid":358954,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔讀書會少左好多門路，necessary but not sufficient.</blockquote><br />\n讀書讀得叻，有獎學金，一毫子學費唔洗俾，仲有錢俾返屋企都得。入神科，好似醫生將來一出身最少三四萬。<br />\n<br />\n讀書真係算係最容易賺錢的方法，係可能悶姐。"}]}